data.description: Enjoy country living just minutes from town.  This 1811 square foot home has two baths, a detached garage/shop on 1.25 acres.  There are 28 mature pecan trees on the property, in addition to fruit trees and additional pecan trees.  Horses are allowed.  The kitchen and bathrooms have been remodeled.  There is tile throughout, except the master bedroom, which is being tiled.    The home has a newer roof.  Don't miss this unique opportunity.
